project:
The main objective of Agawan Base is to be the last person with the games currency, troops! Play by buying properties, accomplishing minigames, and getting troops from opponents! You win the game once your opponent runs out of troops. 

Landing on an enemy-owned property leads you to one of two paths  lose a certain number of troops, or take a gamble at a minigame.

Landing on a mystery space gives a random effect to the player, including losing/gaining troops, or collecting minigame immunities.

Like in Monopoly, you get to own properties that show the different landmarks in Makati City. Our game has similarities in Mario Party, such as coins.

This game is inspired by Puzzle Freak, Monopoly and Mario Party. Puzzle Freak features puzzles that players must solve in order to go through the game. In our game, we added not just puzzles but also other minigames.
